::Prowl::

Prowl's eyes widen as he hears Shadow Wing's comment. "No no, I'm only in 
charge temporarily. Untill Iron Raptor gets back."

He turns to Lunarpine and nods. "Allright. You can go with him," he says.

"Rhinox, can you then stay and help repair?"

Prowl looks at Bluestreak, a frown almost crossing his face. He had the 
feeling he knew this bot from somewhere.....

"The preds attacked again. Can you guys help repair?"
